column5: looking for fishing and resort info on this lodge.. main lake and outposts. thanks

Frank and Renee Evans 4335 Valley Drive NW Rochester, Mn. 55901 Atikwa Lake Lodge owners: 1-800-680-8423 This was true up to about a year ago. They are nice poeple and would gladly send you all the info. you would want. Used to stay with them when they owned a camp on Gullrock lake. Hope this helps. thebronco
Did a search, disregaurd above email and try atikwalakelodge.com. went right to their new web site with new owners listed. thebronco
